{"tid":1966623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭 : 中共駐外使館是在外港人的伙伴 感謝黨的關懷和照顧","createTime":"2020-04-10T10:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T10:57:54.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"595acf79083530ab11ffc6c61a74dd9b919913c7","tid":1966623,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T10:12:23.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥再感謝各部門援助「鑽石公主號」上港人<br />\n10.04.2020 18:06<br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，最後一名因在「鑽石公主號」郵輪上感染新型冠狀病毒而在日本留醫的港人，今日已經返港；在日本協助患者的入境處人員已經撤離當地。行政長官林鄭月娥在社交網站貼文，回顧援助船上港人的行動，指行動能順利完成全賴多個部門，包括入境處、食衛局、衛生署等群策群力，對他們感到自豪，又感謝外交部駐港特派員公署和中國駐日大使館在行動中的支持、日本當局的配合，以及機管局及航空公司的協助。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又表示，公署及國家駐外使館是在外港人的伙伴，形容國家給予的關懷和照顧，正是一國兩制下港人的最佳保障。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279992&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279992%26csid%3D261_341&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6xV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=d1823d64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279992&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"0524afdfaba048eb26e51c8be423db604f0825d3","tid":1966623,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T10:12:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">【國際戰線，靠你支持！】</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\">頂住人民幣，對抗大外宣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>為美國醫護捐贈醫療物資</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://charity.gofundme.com/o/en/campaign/masks-empowerment-campaign\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcharity.gofundme.com%2Fo%2Fen%2Fcampaign%2Fmasks-empowerment-campaign&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6xV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=e31e1fd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://charity.